To derive Equation 3 from Equations 1 and 2, follow these steps:

1. **Substitute the reward function (Equation 2) into the Bradley-Terry model (Equation 1):**
   \begin{align*}
     p^*(y_1 \succ y_2 \mid x) &= \frac{\exp\left(r^*(x, y_1)\right)}{\exp\left(r^*(x, y_1)\right) + \exp\left(r^*(x, y_2)\right)} \\
